node.text:
Please swipe through. Continued below. ******
This may be your first impression of me. You may not have even known, and may attach this stigma to me. You may know the person. You may have already known and silently edged away from me, without knowing the facts. You are entitled to your own choice. But I hope I have opened your eyes on the issue. 
If you're still reading, I'd like to thank each and every one of you who has been there for me. Provided a shoulder to lean on. Given an ear to speak to. 
I vow that no one has to go through any of this. Thank you for reading, and let us all lift the carpet on this issue which has so often been brushed under it. - Kumaran

Please share. 
#MenToo
#MenTooMovement
#MenToogether
#MeToo
Haters gonna hate bro fuck em.
🙏🏾🙏🏾🙏🏾 Stay focused 🙏🏾 just like a bow and arrow, something /someone needs to pull it back to its end before the arrow is able to reach to farther heights/targets !
Love how you can be so honest man. Respect bro. I'll read it all through
I am so sorry that you have been through something lile this. Though I am a woman and not into these feminism movements, I can emphathise in what you feel and go through. In support #MenToo
You're a man of honour, dignity & someone I always have & always will respect highly. This just epitomises why. Forever by your side bro ❤️
@zmakeupz being falsely accused is also incredibly hard to go through, I can’t imagine you have been falsely accused as your a woman so you don’t have to worry about it

@zmakeupz of course your a women you won’t understand how your life can all fall apart by only a mere accusation, I’m not saying rape isn’t horrible it is it truly is but an accusation on such a heinous crime you didn’t commit can make you lose your job, your friends, family, you will be seen as a rapist even if your proven innocent, it’s crazy how many lives have been destroyed merely because a women who wanted attention or wanted revenge decided to use the #METOO movement as a safety net and a launcher for her disgusting act, so please do tell those men who have been jailed for years for a crime they didn’t commit, go tell the 5 African American boys who were accused of beating and raping a women in the New York Central Park, spending 18-20 years in jail before they were released when the real perpetrator came forward, tell the football star of a high school who was accused of rape and lost his football scholarship to play for a university even when he was proven innocent he was downgraded hated and mistreated, he was never given a chance at football again, he beared the tag of rapist even when he was proven to had nothing to do with the girl in question

@zmakeupz you don’t the feeling of being falsely accused and being sent to somewhere where you don’t get to see your parents for months.. your career gets destroyed.. no good company gives you job.. #Mentoo

Way to turn something about people finally standing up for themselves and against their abusers about you. Yes Being falsely accused must not be the best feeling in the world but you cannot imagine the torment people go through after being raped.
Well said. You explained a situation faced by many people every day very well.
Be strong and fight for you reputation.
I’m so sorry you have been accused of such disgusting thing. Love the post! Spread the word 👏🏼👏🏼👏🏼
That’s fucked bro :/ I’m sorry you gotta go through this bullshit
I've had close friends go through this man. Keep your head up. ✊✊✊
